CatDescriptText: Sign on back wall reads: "Ladies Auxiliary of the I. P. P. League cordially invites you to a banquet given in honor of the resident Dr. George L. Winstead, at this club, Monday June 30th, 1947..."
TitMainTitle: Women and men seated around banquet tables in interior with sign on back wall reading "Ladies Auxiliary of the I. P. P. League..."
